entries.journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has employed you. It's usually a good idea to do what he suggests. People that don't play their cards right against Fett have a habit of catching a case of death.
entries.journal_entry_title: Working for Boba Fett, phase V
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the Dearic hotel on Talus and have a chat with the leader of 'The Claw', one way or the other.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Claw thugs are attacking you! Defeat them and gain access to their leader.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Find out what the leader of 'the Claw', Imbrimi, knows about Durge.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Travel to Dee'Ja peak on Naboo and try to find the abandoned building that Durge was last hiding in.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You must be very close if one of his droids are after you. Destroy it.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Looks like you need to defeat this droid as well.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Durge must be close! Check buildings. If you find him, defeat him and bring back his helmet as proof to Fett.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Durge has ambushed you! Terminate him and get his helmet to prove what you've done to Boba Fett.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return Durge's helmet to Fett. Even he should be impressed after this... or maybe not.
